Name: UFO穿越 （UFO Cross）
About the game: 《UFO Cross》In 2025, a space ship came to the earth, there are a number of exiled space criminals, the spaceship circled in the sky, and the criminals have been released around the world, with their arrival, the electrical and mechanical equipment around the world stopped working, the universe criminals in the earth to commit crimes, massacre of human beings.Save the world! Main Features: Third-person 3D shooters， The mission objective is to fight a group of cosmic hooligans, destroy their jammers and escape. You only have one life. If you die, you have to start all over again. Headquarters will provide you with a batch of ammunition, can complete the task depends on you, good luck!
